snippet: The patient, who an official said was not showing symptoms, arrived in Omaha on Sunday to be monitored at the same hospital that previously treated three patients who contracted Ebola overseas.
lead_paragraph: The patient, who an official said was not showing symptoms, arrived in Omaha on Sunday to be monitored at the same hospital that previously treated three patients who contracted Ebola overseas.

headline.main: U.S. Health Worker Exposed to Ebola in Sierra Leone Arrives in Nebraska
